    "name": "The Chronicles of Overlord",
    "steam_appid": 2150210,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150210/extras/272cc06586d1a40d563713ef55a014f0.avif?t=1770992769\" width=630 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《The Chronicles of Overlord》是一款战术角色扮演游戏，故事发生在一个被人族、精灵、兽人及其他种族间的战争所撕裂的世界。一股被称为“吞噬者”的古老邪恶威胁要吞噬整个世界，而唯有霸王——一位复苏的死灵术大师——意识到了这场迫近的灾难。为了阻止所有生命的灭绝，他必须夺取四件传说中的神器，每件神器都由各自种族的强大统治者所守护。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>深度战术玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个关卡都是一项新的挑战，需要独特的策略。掌握深思熟虑的阵型站位，结合英雄们的技能与法术，并巧妙地运用神器与魔法药剂来主宰战场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150210/extras/f94b654dee8a639551107b86787617ec.poster.avif?t=1770992769\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150210/extras/f94b654dee8a639551107b86787617ec.webm?t=1770992769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150210/extras/f94b654dee8a639551107b86787617ec.mp4?t=1770992769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特的英雄与能力</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指挥一群各具特色的英雄，每位都拥有独特的技能组合和战斗角色。深入的角色成长系统让你能适应各种战况，并对不可预测的局势做出有效反应。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150210/extras/eb7955a61b209cd4eb06136076e37761.poster.avif?t=1770992769\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150210/extras/eb7955a61b209cd4eb06136076e37761.webm?t=1770992769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150210/extras/eb7955a61b209cd4eb06136076e37761.mp4?t=1770992769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富的奇幻世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸于一个原創的奇幻设定中，这个世界拥有连贯的结构与截然不同的势力阵营，每个阵营都有其独特的战争理念。通过带有选项的对话和沉浸式的过场动画，让你更深地融入霸王的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150210/extras/5df052b2504d93680d44105f089f556a.poster.avif?t=1770992769\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150210/extras/5df052b2504d93680d44105f089f556a.webm?t=1770992769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150210/extras/5df052b2504d93680d44105f089f556a.mp4?t=1770992769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>现代的像素美术</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验经典像素美术与现代视觉效果的绝妙融合。动态光影、精细的法术动画及精心设计的场景，赋予游戏极具表现力且符合当代审美的视觉呈现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150210/extras/338ba002454a07dd160dac723fbd69de.avif?t=1770992769\" width=1560 height=1122 /></span></p>",
